Sample beta values

Source: R/sub02.R
sub02.Rd

Example dataset for testing analyses, and to see input structure

sub02

Format

Objects of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) a minimal tibble for the vtuner analysis (53856 x 7)

sub

factor ID of subject

run

factor ID of run

voxel

factor ID of voxel

contrast

Factor with different values of contrast. Note that the factor must have the lower levels of contrast correspond to a lower integer representation (e.g., low == 1 and high == 2)

orientation

Orientation presented on trial (-pi,pi)

y

beta values in given condition (corresponds to beta in betas2)

ses

factor id of session in which run was collected

Value

a tibble
